snippet.title: Astro Prospector - Teaser
snippet.description:
Astro Prospector is an incremental bullet heaven about mining asteroids and fighting SpaceCorp. Collect resources, upgrade your ship and become unstoppable. Return AstroCoffee to humanity!

Wishlist now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3503440/Astro_Prospector/

Made by Incrementalist Games.
